it.polimi.se2019.server.model

Class GameMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.se2019.server.model.GameMap

  • public class GameMap
extends Object
    This class defines the map used throughout the game. The map is created during the set up phase after obtaining the most voted map. All the loot and spawn tiles are stored and each map has a graph that allows an efficient calculation of the distance between each tile.
